From: Nandha Kishore Easwaran <nandhaki@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Mon, 4 Aug 2025 10:11:06 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 4/8] UPSTREAM: DP: Move pdev alloc into arch specific function

Move pdev alloc into arch specific function since there is a difference
in refill and htt setup logic between different architectures.

Dependencies:
0500-0003-UPSTREAM-DP-Define-arch-specific-link-desc-size.patch

Signed-off-by: Nandha Kishore Easwaran <nandhaki@qti.qualcomm.com>
